Package: sportsdata
Type: Package
Title: Imports and provided descriptive statistics on sports data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Warren Hyson
Maintainer: Warren C Hyson <warrenhyson@mail.usf.edu>s
Description: The goal of this package is for sports fans to have a easy way to get data from all years for their favorite sports including; Hockey(NHL), Football(NFL), and Basketball(NBA). 
Additonally, there will be built in functions for creating simple graphs and retriving statistics so that non-coders can have a easy time getting data on thier favorite teams.
License: CCO
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
